        "id": 5230
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-06-14T20:01:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Right - an upcoming CL adds a scissor rect and, since these are implicitly intersection clips, only the pixels outside the clips but inside the scissor are written.",
      "parentUuid": "f6b821b2_15a96d85",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 195,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 201,
        "endChar": 5
      },
      "revId": "30d81895e1110a8280ee2c5359cfdd2f0692bf5a",
